{"tid":1441482,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"idiot 的原意是「不關心政治的人」","createTime":"2019-08-10T16:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T20:40:15.000Z","uid":5866,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22c757290640f2e31178095377ec6823e55bf5cb","tid":1441482,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2293236250991978&amp;id=1747417885573820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2293236250991978%26id%3D1747417885573820&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=51538be8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2293236250991978&amp;id=1747417885573820</a><br />\n<br />\n「#白癡」的英文 #idiot<br />\n源自希臘文的 &iota;&delta;&iota;ώ&tau;&eta;&sigmaf; (idiotes)：<br />\n字根idios，有「私人、個人」的意思<br />\n而在最早實行民主制度的希臘城邦--雅典<br />\n這字則專指那些「不去參加公民大會的人」<br />\n<br />\n因為對雅典人來說，一個合格的 #公民<br />\n應該要在個人工作和日常生活之外<br />\n另外花心思去關心或參與公眾事務<br />\n所以那些 #不想碰政治的人<br />\n就因此被叫成了「&iota;&delta;&iota;ώ&tau;&eta;&sigmaf;」<br />\n以表示他和一般優質公民的不同<br />\n<br />\n雖然這字一開始並沒有白癡的意思*<br />\n但因為雅典公民好像還滿賭爛這種人<br />\n如果隨便罵人&iota;&delta;&iota;ώ&tau;&eta;&sigmaf;，我猜仍有可能被告<br />\n例如在希臘歷史上，最著名的一段政治演說 --《伯里克里斯陣亡將士葬禮演說》中就提到：<br />\n「儘管雅典公民們都有個人的事業要忙<br />\n但在公眾事務上還是有能力做出正確決斷<br />\n至於那些捨棄公民職責、不理政治的人<br />\n他們絕不是沒有野心--而是沒有用。」<br />\n<br />\n嗯，請大家一定在民主社會中做個有用的人。<br />\n<br />\n*註：idiot這個字一開始並沒有什麼貶義<br />\n是經過了往後多種語言的借用與演化後<br />\n才慢慢具有負面意義。像在拉丁文<br />\nidiot有文盲、沒受過教育的意思<br />\n中世紀法文則用這字表示愚笨<br />\n然後才有了英文中的「白癡」"},{"pid":"28335b60ed38ea5acb4c97d6dd08a4c2b0c0d332","tid":1441482,"uid":5866,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"Source: 如上<br />\n原文post主回覆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n什麼是政治？我自己最喜歡的解釋是：「政治就是在為社會價值做權威性的分配」。<br />\n　　<br />\n包含水和土地，所有有價值的資源，在人類社會中都必然要面臨分配的問題。但該怎麼分配，才能讓這些資源產出最大價值、而且不會引發社會衝突，這整個過程中的每一個環節，都是政治。<br />\n　　<br />\n只要生活在這社會，你所使用的資源，都必然經過了政治這道分配程序 (可能只有空氣和陽光不用)，這就是為什麼我們說生活即政治。<br />\n　　<br />\n其實圖上的標語本來是長成下面這樣的，但因為我們更想強調政治即生活，所以才把標語換成更生活化的東西。最後我還是要在此呼籲--<br />\n　　<br />\n堅持一粽原則，只有南部粽才是真正的粽子，謝謝。<br />\n　　<br />\n這次的參考資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Idiot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIdiot&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=6a3c16c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Idiot</a> (wiki)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ichentsai.md/photos/p.2277934972276022/2277934972276022/?type=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fichentsai.md%2Fphotos%2Fp.2277934972276022%2F2277934972276022%2F%3Ftype%3D1&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=54cbedbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ichentsai.md/photos/p.2277934972276022/2277934972276022/?type=1</a> ( 蔡依橙的閱讀筆記原文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ancient-origins.net/history-important-events/idiots-greek-democracy-0011534\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ancient-origins.net%2Fhistory-important-events%2Fidiots-greek-democracy-0011534&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=47bbae91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ancient-origins.net/history-important-events/idiots-greek-democracy-0011534</a> (英文專文)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.constitution.org/gr/pericles_funeral_oration.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitution.org%2Fgr%2Fpericles_funeral_oration.htm&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=69a2cca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.constitution.org/gr/pericles_funeral_oration.htm</a> (《伯里克里斯陣亡將士葬禮演說》英文譯文)"},{"pid":"82d17798b1a94312a93e95a0b1264cf108e866c1","tid":1441482,"uid":5866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLDBXWs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLDBXWs.jpg&h=e89c701e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79b68eaa2702370aa188111b6da99a2db340d822","tid":1441482,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67c7608f9978fbf582ef6b2c49b53c64cfc1e7fb","tid":1441482,"uid":209468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8a5bda9d47be9613296b7659692319c2c816d1a4","tid":1441482,"uid":209468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63984f5474584e5f8512ce41e99b9416501e2022","tid":1441482,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:25:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190712/20726425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190712%2F20726425&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=f401b52b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190712%2F20726425&h=9a2dd73c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190712/20726425</a>"},{"pid":"77ff17c1c0af5b654b75ae7e9d24e7462003f23b","tid":1441482,"uid":209468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a434a6a9164869f32a4243a6ebc8be1ba4b55281","tid":1441482,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:40:15.000Z","msg":"Here each individual is interested not only in his own affairs but in the affairs of the state as well: even those who are mostly occupied with their own business are extremely well-informed on general politics&mdash;this is a peculiarity of ours: <span style=\"color: red;\">we do not say that a man who takes no interest in politics<br />\nis a man who minds his own business; we say that he has no business here at all. </span>"}]}